 will be available in-game along with the 1.42 update.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All players will receive a copy of this relic in a free bundle which is set to accompany the client release.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Ron_abacus.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1495\" width=\"500\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Ron_abacus.png 667w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Ron_abacus-300x196.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>PANTHEON COLLECTIONS<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A number of exciting new Collections will become available to players immediately after updating to 1.42:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>War Gods I Update<ul><li>Ares<\/li><li>Frigg<\/li><li>Hachiman<\/li><li>Sekhmet<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/warrior_ring-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1496\" width=\"451\" height=\"458\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/warrior_ring-1.png 601w, https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/warrior_ring-1-296x300.png 296w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 451px) 100vw, 451px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<ol start=\"2\"><li>War Gods II<ul><li>Achilles<\/li><li>Nergal<\/li><li>Tengu<\/li><li>Totec<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/spirit_war-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1497\" width=\"456\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"https:\